	   <tr><td colspan=2>The coin in Oggok is in the big pond. You must jump in and swim around and look. Its there, for I have it. It took a while but I found it on the bottom. In Grobb, the coin is located between the Warriors Guild and the merchant(selling alcohol and bags). There are 2 little pools of water there and it is in one of them. Presently, I am of 12 seasons and I have acquired 8 of the ten coins necessary for this Quest. Last on my list are Halas and Erudin. I used invis while getting most of these coins, since I am a Dark Elf and with Innoruuk as my God. The dwarves will attack if under illusion or at least they did me. Good Luck..<br>Tdayael 12 seasonal Enchanter<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
